 to first explain some basics and then we made also tutorials for all kinds of edits possible. On the other hand, it is not necessary to code and for me, as a person who knows to code a bit but is a manager using Elementor is much faster than coding.\n\nOverall Elementor is a great tool and we like it but if you are to build a more complex site and include some automations, expect it to start to be not super easy (still much easier than coding).</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hakodesh\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ae6948487a09abeaab1518000be51948?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ae6948487a09abeaab1518000be51948?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hakodesh\" class=\"reviewer-name\">hakodesh</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">avril 8, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Is the best plugin!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Nice Plugin!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div