8b76332edf620eb805fc55ae4185f40?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/exigymarketing\" class=\"reviewer-name\">exigymarketing</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">avril 8, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Using Weglot to translate our website to Italian was smooth and easy. Support were also very quick to respond to a query that we encountered. Very satisfied with the quality of the plugin. Definitely recommend this for anyone looking to translate a website :)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/churcholution\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6480b35982429d6ebd5a658c0539437d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6480b35982429d6ebd5a658c0539437d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/churcholution\" class=\"reviewer-name\">churcholution</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">avril 7, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Quick and competent support for a specific issue.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very easy and very good</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mauer59h\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/05533d4816b6b9a30243a03bae506d3d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/05533d4816b6b9a30243a03bae506d3d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mauer59h\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mauer59h</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">avril 7, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">One of the best plugins here on WordPress. Easy and quick to install.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great, great support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/marvin1986\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e839616b8bceed7c59864d90b1c11a01?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e839616b8bceed7c59864d90b1c11a01?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/marvin1986\" class=\"reviewer-name\">marvin1986</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">avril 7, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">First of all, I always try to make work translations with Weglot or WPML for my clients. But I turns out, that Weglot wins a little more each time. It just works perfect even with different plugins shortcodes etc.\n\nAlso, there was CSS issue and John from Weglot solved it within ours and was very friendly and helpful. Great service! Can recommend :)!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">A+ for Complex, Custom Websites</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tderkowski\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d20f99c2d2d63cf4b5229b2b36f4507a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d20f99c2d2d63cf4b5229b2b36f4507a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tderkowski\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Tom <small>(tderkowski)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">avril 3, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I head up development for a bespoke WP shop. All of our work is custom, much of it is interactive. This makes finding a translation system an especially large challenge. Weglot actually kind of...just works. We did have some intricacies that didn\'t quite work out of the box, but Weglot support got everything functioning 100% before we had ever paid a dime.\n\nNever seen a company do so much to please while still in the pre-sale process. And they delivered. The solution is actually not believable to me, to the extent that this is the only review for anything I\'ve ever written.\n\nTo put this in context: Weglot was able to reduce the amount of time required to translate a highly custom site by one month of development hours as compared to WPML. One month. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kaixue\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4b2a50a4